'''Nanak Darbar Indian Sikh Temple, Iloilo''' is an [[Indian people|Indian]] [[Sikh]] temple in [[Iloilo City]], [[Philippines]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.worldgurudwaras.com/phillipines/nanak-darbar-iloilo-inc|title=Nanak Darbar, Iloilo, Inc - Gurudwaras of World|work=Gurudwaras of World}}</ref><ref name="habagatcentral.com">{{cite web|url=http://habagatcentral.com/2010/08/10/sat-siri-akal-spice-and-prayers-at-iloilos-nanak-darbar-temple/|title=Sat Siri Akal: Spice and Prayers at Iloilo's Nanak Darbar Temple - HabagatCentral|work=HabagatCentral}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com.sg/books?id=39lJz_L4MdUC&pg=PA545&lpg=PA545&dq=nanak+darbar+iloilo&source=bl&ots=xaTMClgpbU&sig=ohgLno6WelrUpmgmtFziG0S1Ar0&hl=en&sa=X&ei=Me0sVNfZC4K3uATKloLABw&ved=0CFcQ6AEwDg#v=onepage&q=nanak%20darbar%20iloilo&f=false|title=Rising India and Indian Communities in East Asia|publisher=}}</ref> It was part of creating a Guinness world record, for simultaneous candle lighting by 100,000 people for the world peace,<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.philstar.com/headlines/2014/04/15/1312837/phl-sets-world-record-light-100000-candles-peace|title=Phl sets world record to light 100,000 candles for peace|work=philstar.com}}</ref>

==Location==
It is located close to the [[Old Iloilo Airport]] at 113 R. Mapa Street<ref name="habagatcentral.com"/> in the [[Mandurriao]] district of Iloilo City.<ref name="myphilippinelife.com">{{cite web|url=http://myphilippinelife.com/indian-iloilo/|title=Indian Food in Iloilo|publisher=}}</ref>

==Importance==
{{see also|Hinduism in the Philippines|Religion in pre-colonial Philippines|Indosphere|Indianisation (disambiguation){{!}}Indianisation|List of India-related topics in the Philippines}}

The temple serves the [[Indians in the Philippines|Indian community]] in Iloilo city. It also acts as a means of cultural integration by welcoming all and by providing free meals for all visitors.<ref name="myphilippinelife.com"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://insearchofiloilo.blogspot.sg/2013/01/nanark-darbur-sikh-temple-of-iloilo.html|title=In Search Of Iloilo City|author=Insearchof Iloilo|publisher=}}</ref>

